stanford.cs106.collections

Class Vertex<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • stanford.cs106.collections.Vertex<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<Vertex<V>>

    public class Vertex<V>
extends Observable
implements Comparable<Vertex<V>>, Cloneable
    A Vertex object represents extra information associated with each vertex. Each Vertex object for some vertex value v is accessed internally in a Graph subclass by writing: 
     
 vertexInfo(v)
